一些基督徒認為，藉著信仰，效果較普通之戒毒所好。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://cclw.net/experience/jiedu.htm |title=福音戒毒效果如何 |access-date=2007-10-06 |archive-date=2020-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200203061249/http://cclw.net/experience/jiedu.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

